BIG SHOUT OUT TO SEAN ROONEY AND TRACKMIX STUDIOS IRELAND!!! As trackmix’s post on fb says “Just before Christmas, Sean Rooney (a very talented piano player) sent a classical piano arrangement of one of their songs to artist/band Falling In Reverse. The artist loved it and asked him to record it professionally. Sean came into me and tracked all the piano and strings and percussion and printed the stems and sent them off. It was released yesterday and currently stands at almost 850,000 views.
Big congrats to Sean.
Hopefully it will be a big break for him.” Cannot believe this!!!! CONGRATS SEAN AND RONNIE OMG!!!!
